title: Regular-Season Awards Ballot | Group Chat
description:
Justin and Rob are joined by The Ringer’s Wosny Lambre to discuss who they believe is the MVP of the 2021 season (02:00). Later, they make their picks for Rookie of the Year, Defensive Player of the Year, and more (38:00). 
Hosts: Justin Verrier and Rob Mahoney
Guest: Wosny Lambre
Production Assistant: Jonathan Kermah
